Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:14.12,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{This isn't too weird, is it?}Có lạ không nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.11,0:00:26.77,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I hope my young master notices me.}Hi vọng chủ nhân nhận ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.51,0:02:11.51,sign_2842_3_Episode_4__Does_,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{Episode 4:}{\fsp2}{ Does the Young Master Like Pudding?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:21.70,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{How did it come to this?}Sao chuyện này lại xảy ra?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.69,0:02:27.20,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I want the young master to grow up healthy \Nand well, both physically and emotionally.}Mình muốn chủ nhân trưởng thành cả về thể xác lẫn tâm hồn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:30.86,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{That's why I came to this mansion.}Thế nên mình đã đến dinh thự này.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.31,0:02:35.55,Flashback - Sus Maid,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Would you be so kind as \Nto hire me at this mansion?}Liệu ngài có thể thuê tôi được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:39.14,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It was, but...}Đáng ra là như vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:42.96,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{He's so suspicious of me.}Ngài ấy nghĩ mình làm gì đó mờ ám.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:46.09,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I can't blame him.}Cũng chịu thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:48.66,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I did just barge in on him.}Tự nhiên mình xuất hiện mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:53.52,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{But at this rate, I'm going to \Nhave a negative influence on him.}Nhưng cứ thế này, sẽ ảnh hưởng tiêu cực đến chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:03:00.37,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{For him to grow up healthy, \NI need to get closer to him.}Để phát triển khoẻ mạnh, phải thân thiết hơn nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.13,0:03:07.79,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Watching over the young master is \Nmy duty as a maid and a grown-up.}Quan sát chủ nhân trưởng thành là nhiệm vụ củ mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:23.34,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What have you been doing \Nall this time, Lilith?}Nãy tới giờ cô làm gì thế hả, Lilith?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:24.73,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Y-Young master...}C-Chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:27.16,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Why are you monitoring me?}Định quan sát tôi đấy hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:28.14,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Um...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.01,0:03:30.29,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'm...}Tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:35.43,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You're always watching me, too, though.}Ngài lúc nào cũng quan sát tôi mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:38.38,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're looking for my \Nweaknesses, aren't you?!}Cô đang tìm điểm yếu của tôi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:39.96,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I won't let you!}Đừng hòng!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:41.61,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master, wait!}Chủ nhân, khoan đã!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:45.81,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Lilith!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:54.28,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Ow...}Đau...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:56.54,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry, young master!}Chủ nhân, tôi xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:58.50,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Are you all right?}Ngài ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:03.68,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I need to watch over you, don't I?}Quả nhiên phải để ý đến cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:10.19,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I won't run away, and I won't let you go.}Tôi không chạy đâu, và cũng không buông cô đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:13.18,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Right.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:21.77,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'm trying to get closer to him,}Mình cố gắng gần gũi với chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.77,0:04:23.89,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{but I just landed on top of him instead.}nhưng cuối cùng lại đè lên người ngài ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:31.15,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Look at that frown...}Ánh mắt khó chịu đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:37.12,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I have to redeem myself,}Không, phải chuộc lỗi,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:40.50,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{by being more grown-up and maid-like.}bằng việc trở nên trưởng thành và ra dáng hầu gái.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.00,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master...}Chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:52.81,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Don't you get bored watching me so much?}Ngài không chán khi nhìn tôi mãi sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:57.32,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{That came across as grown-up, didn't it?}Nói chuyện kiểu trưởng thành thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:04:58.54,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Suspicious!}Quá đáng ngờ!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:04.68,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're trying to divert my attention so you \Ncan get away with your insidious plots!}Cô đánh lạc hướng tôi để âm mưu gì phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:06.07,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I-I'm not...}K-Không phải...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:08.81,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{H-Here we go...}C-Cứ thế này...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:13.41,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're beautiful when you're \Nworking, too, you know.}Với cả cô đẹp tuyệt vời khi làm việc nhà.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:17.52,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{No matter where I look from, no matter \Nwhat you're doing, I won't get bored.}Dù có nhìn cô mãi tôi cũng không chán.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:20.12,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I could watch you for hours and hours!}Tôi có thể quan sát cả ngày!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.12,0:05:22.41,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{J-Just like I thought...}Q-Quả nhiên!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,0:05:24.49,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I wish I could watch you my whole life!}Tôi muốn được nhìn cô suốt đời!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:29.28,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{That's good, then.}Vậy thì may quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:32.26,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's not good!}Không ổn chút nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.01,0:05:36.32,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I can't.}Không được...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:42.00,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{He's so honest, I can't behave \Nlike a well-composed adult.}Chủ nhân quá thẳng thắn,\N làm mình không thể điềm đạm được.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:45.90,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Next time...}Lần tới nhất định...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.09,0:05:57.13,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{First, I need to get his guard down.}Đầu tiên phải giảm sự cảnh giác của chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.57,0:05:59.23,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{For that...}Để được như thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:02.17,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'm going to demonstrate that I'm \Na dependable, grown-up maid.}Mình phải chứng minh bản thân là một hầu gái hữu dụng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:05.44,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master...}Chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:11.58,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I know all about your feelings.}Tôi biết rõ cảm xúc của ngài mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:17.83,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Suspicious!}Quá đáng ngờ!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:19.54,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Huh?!}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:23.88,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I was just trying to tell \Nhim that I understand him.}Mình muốn nói mình hiểu rõ chủ nhân thôi mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:25.64,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Wait...}Không lẽ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:28.64,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You know that I want to \Nget to know you better...}Cô biết rằng tôi muốn biết về cô nhiều hơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:31.86,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That you're all I ever think about...}Và trong đầu tôi chỉ nghĩ về cô...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.86,0:06:33.78,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You see through all of that?!}Cô đã biết tất cả sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:35.85,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{This wasn't the plan!}Không phải thế này...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:41.78,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm right, aren't I?}Đúng rồi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:43.38,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're definitely suspicious.}Quả nhiên quá đáng ngờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:54.59,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I blew it again!}Mình lại thế rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.15,0:06:58.31,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I just want to get closer \Nto the young master,}Mình chỉ muốn gần gũi với chủ nhân thôi,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:07:01.71,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{yet I'm getting nowhere.}vậy mà lúc nào cũng làm rối tung lên.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:06.41,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's not that he hates me, I'm sure...}Chắc hẳn ngài ấy không ghét mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.43,0:07:11.55,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{But he's never going to \Ntrust me if this keeps up.}Nhưng cứ thế này chủ nhân sẽ không tin tưởng mình mất.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:17.10,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{There has to be a way.}Phải có cách nào đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:21.85,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{A way to gain his trust \Nand become closer to him.}Cách để chủ nhân giảm cảnh giác và gần gũi với mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:26.45,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Play?}Chơi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:27.44,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:30.07,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{We may as well, since we're \Nboth here in the mansion.}Dù gì cũng có hai người.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:32.33,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{How about a change of pace?}Chúng ta làm gì đó đổi không khí đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:37.06,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Play is surely the best way \Nto relate to each other.}Chơi đùa cùng nhau là cách dễ nhất để thấu hiểu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:38.43,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Sure.}Được.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:43.56,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{We'll have lots of fun, just the two of us.}Chúng ta sẽ cùng nhau chơi thật nhiều trò vui nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:47.48,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Well?}Sao nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:51.07,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{That was a good, grown-up \Ninvitation, wasn't it?}Mình đã mời một cách rất người lớn đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:54.64,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{More fun than now?}Vui hơn nữa á?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:59.45,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{But I'm already having plenty \Nof fun since you came.}Nhưng tôi đã rất vui khi cô đến đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:03.48,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm having fun whenever you're around.}Miễn có cô bên cạnh là vui rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:06.45,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Wait...}Không lẽ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:08.28,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Is this part of your trap, too?}Đây cũng là bẫy cô đặt ra?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:09.80,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Why...}Tại sao...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:13.07,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're enjoying making \Nme suspicious of you...}Cô tận hưởng cảm giác nghi ngờ của tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:14.93,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Wait, huh?}Ủa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:15.92,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master...}Chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:18.26,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{He's confused himself with his own words.}Ngài ấy đang hoang mang vì những gì đã nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:20.06,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What does that mean?!}Vậy là sao hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.59,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{That's my line!}Câu đó tôi nói chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.22,0:08:25.95,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I-I'm sure we'll understand \Nif we play together.}T-Tôi chắc nếu cùng nhau chơi thì sẽ hiểu thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.95,0:08:28.51,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Let's play your favorite game.}Hãy chơi trò chủ nhân thích đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:30.00,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Really?}Thật hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:31.21,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{In that case...}Vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:35.08,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It's your turn.}Tớ cô đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:36.10,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Right.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:44.41,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master?}Chủ nhân?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:49.66,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{This is the one game my father taught me.}Đây là trò mà ba tôi đã chỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:55.47,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{My mother and father were very kind people,}Ba mẹ tôi là người rất dịu dàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:58.27,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{but they were always busy.}Nhưng họ luôn bận rộn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:09:00.19,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{They were rarely home.}Hiếm khi về nhà.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:01.95,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{So...}Thế nên...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:08.13,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I was happy whenever they were here.}Miễn họ có ở nhà là tôi vui rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:14.52,Flashback - Sus Maid,Mom,0,0,0,,{Nope.}Không được.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:15.69,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{No!}Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.69,0:09:17.95,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I want to play with Father!}Con muốn chơi với ba!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:24.44,Flashback - Sus Maid,Mom,0,0,0,,{Yuuri, Dad's at home today, \Nbut he has to work.}Yuuri, ba con hôm nay ở nhà \Nnhưng vẫn phải làm việc.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.62,0:09:32.07,Flashback - Sus Maid,Mom,0,0,0,,{I know.}Phải rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:34.44,Flashback - Sus Maid,Mom,0,0,0,,{Why don't you play with me today?}Hôm nay chơi với mẹ nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:38.12,Flashback - Sus Maid,Mom,0,0,0,,{We can make the pudding that \Nyou and your dad both like.}Chúng ta sẽ làm bánh pudding ba con thích.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:38.88,Flashback - Sus Maid,Mom,0,0,0,,{Okay?}Được chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:43.08,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Father said you don't know how to cook.}Ba nói mẹ không biết nấu ăn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:47.75,Flashback - Sus Maid,Mom,0,0,0,,Được rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:52.58,Flashback - Sus Maid,Mom,0,0,0,,{I'll make the very best pudding \Nand make him admit that it's delicious!}Mẹ sẽ làm món puding ngon nhất cho ba con xem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:10:00.72,Flashback - Sus Maid,Mom,0,0,0,,Đừng phá ba con làm việc đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:18.60,Flashback - Sus Maid,Dad,0,0,0,,Yuuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:31.57,Flashback - Sus Maid,Mom,0,0,0,,{I hope Yuuri's being a good boy.}Hi vọng Yuuri ngoan ngoãn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.51,0:10:33.40,Flashback - Sus Maid,Dad,0,0,0,,King.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:34.32,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,King.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:35.50,Flashback - Sus Maid,Dad,0,0,0,,Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:36.54,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:37.37,Flashback - Sus Maid,Dad,0,0,0,,Pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.37,0:10:38.29,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Bawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:43.11,Flashback - Sus Maid,Dad,0,0,0,,{Yuuri, it's "pawn," not "bawn."}Yuuri, là Pawn, không phải Bawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:45.24,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:47.18,Flashback - Sus Maid,Dad,0,0,0,,{That's right. Good job.}Đúng rồi, giỏi lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.95,0:10:50.71,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're the king, Father.}Ba là King.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:53.44,Flashback - Sus Maid,Dad,0,0,0,,{That would make Mother the queen.}Vậy thì mẹ là Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:57.55,Flashback - Sus Maid,Dad,0,0,0,,{By the way, the queen is the \Nstrongest piece in all of chess.}Trên bàn cờ thì quân Queen là mạnh nhất.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:10:59.53,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Stronger than the king?}Mạnh hơn cả King?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:01.55,Flashback - Sus Maid,Dad,0,0,0,,{That's right, stronger than the king.}Phải, hơn cả King.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:06.25,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{So Mother's the strongest \Nin the family, then?}Vậy mẹ mạnh nhất gia đình ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:08.79,Flashback - Sus Maid,Dad,0,0,0,,{I suppose so.}Đúng nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:10.37,Flashback - Sus Maid,Mom,0,0,0,,Yuuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:14.89,Flashback - Sus Maid,Mom,0,0,0,,{I knew you'd be in here.}Biết ngay mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:19.88,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{But I want to play with Father.}Nhưng con muốn chơi với ba.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:21.93,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry.}Con xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:23.89,Flashback - Sus Maid,Dad,0,0,0,,{Come on, Shiho.}Thôi nào Shiho.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:26.16,Flashback - Sus Maid,Dad,0,0,0,,{Yuuri says he's sorry.}Yuuri biết lỗi rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:28.19,Flashback - Sus Maid,Mom,0,0,0,,{And you, honey.}Cả anh nữa đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.19,0:11:30.41,Flashback - Sus Maid,Mom,0,0,0,,{You always spoil Yuuri.}Đừng có chiều con nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:33.07,Flashback - Sus Maid,Dad,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry.}Anh xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:36.75,Flashback - Sus Maid,Mom,0,0,0,,{Just this once.}Lần cuối nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:46.42,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Mother, Father taught me chess.}Mẹ, ba dạy con chơi cờ đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:50.13,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{He says you're the queen.}Ba nói mẹ là Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:55.47,Flashback - Sus Maid,Dad,0,0,0,,{We were just saying you're \Nbeautiful, like a queen.}Ý anh là em đẹp như nữ hoàng vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.47,0:11:58.31,Flashback - Sus Maid,Mom,0,0,0,,{Aw, you're embarrassing me.}Xấu hổ quá đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:03.55,Flashback - Sus Maid,Dad,0,0,0,,{Anyway, was there something you wanted?}Mà em có chuyện gì hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.90,Flashback - Sus Maid,Mom,0,0,0,,{Right.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:06.29,Flashback - Sus Maid,Mom,0,0,0,,{I made some pudding.}Em có làm pudding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:07.82,Flashback - Sus Maid,Mom,0,0,0,,{Why don't you both come for tea?}Sao hai ba con không ra ăn thử?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:14.44,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm hungry!}Con đói rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:26.29,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I only played chess with \Nmy father a few times,}Tôi chỉ chơi cờ với ba mình vài lần,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:29.68,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{but it was fun.}nhưng nó thực sự rất vui.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:37.93,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master, I'm here.}Chủ nhân, có tôi rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:41.18,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'll play you whenever \Nyou'd like from now on.}Từ giờ tôi sẽ chơi với ngài bất cứ lúc nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:43.56,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Lilith...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:58.80,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm good at this, you know.}Tôi mạnh lắm đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:13:00.37,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Watch me beat you, Lilith.}Thi đấu đi, Lilith!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:03.96,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Not without a fight, Master Yuuri.}Tôi không thua đâu, chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:08.91,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Maybe I was getting too anxious.}Có lẽ mình đã hơi vội vàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:14.07,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'll just do what I can, little by little,}Cứ từ từ làm những việc mình có thể.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:18.84,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{so that the young master will smile more.}Thì chủ nhân nhất định sẽ mở lòng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:32.31,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master, I did say we should \Nhave fun, but... it's getting...}Chủ nhân, tôi rất vui nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:33.36,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{One more!}Trận nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:34.92,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{We're playing one more game!}Thêm ván nữa đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:40.65,Main,Student A,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:41.58,Main,Student B,0,0,0,,{Bye.}Chào nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:14:00.21,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Maybe I'll make pudding today.}Hôm nay làm pudding nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:02.56,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'm sure the young master \Nwill enjoy it, too.}Chủ nhân sẽ thích lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:09.14,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Welcome home, young master.}Mừng ngài trở về.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:11.48,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Thanks.}Tôi về rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:14.75,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master?}Chủ nhân?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:26.62,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It turned out quite well.}Khá là ổn đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:33.16,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{The young master appeared a bit down \Nearlier, but hopefully this pudding...}Chủ nhân lúc nãy có vẻ không khoẻ, nếu ăn pudding vào...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:36.04,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It's suspicious that you'd \Nsuddenly serve pudding!}Tự nhiên làm pudding, quá đáng ngờ!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:37.81,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What are you scheming?!}Cô định làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:41.77,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I thought you might want some pudding.}Tôi tưởng ngài muốn ăn chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:44.02,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What are you, Lilith? A psychic?}Cô là gì vậy? Siêu năng lực hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:46.77,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{How could you know what I wanted?}Sao cô biết tôi muốn ăn?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:47.70,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Delicious!}Ngon quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:49.43,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{There's more, if you'd like.}Vẫn còn đó ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:52.22,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{No doubt about it.}Chắc chắn là thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:14:57.37,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah?}Sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:15:00.20,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I made pudding for snack time.}Tôi có làm pudding đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:01.40,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Would you like some?}Ngài muốn dùng chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:05.82,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's hand-made.}Là tôi tự làm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:07.71,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Thanks.}Cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.46,0:15:17.13,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{The young master isn't suspicious of me?!}Chủ nhân không nói mình đáng ngờ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:20.80,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's a good thing that he \Nisn't suspicious of me.}Là điều tốt nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.16,0:15:24.28,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{This is the way it ought to be \Nbetween a maid and her master.}Đây mới chính là quan hệ chủ tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.28,0:15:28.01,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{The young master can grow up healthy now...}Chủ nhân sẽ có thể phát triển khoẻ mạnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.81,0:15:29.83,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:35.86,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I still want him to be suspicious of me!}Mình vẫn muốn chủ nhân nói mình đáng ngờ!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:38.91,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're suspicious, following me around!}Cô quá đáng ngờ! Bám theo tôi suốt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.18,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{This should do it.}Phải như thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.43,0:15:48.21,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{He didn't notice me!}Chủ nhân không nhận ra?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:51.59,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{He's always so alert.}Mọi khi cảnh giác lắm mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:52.90,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{What's going on?!}Chuyện gì đang xảy ra?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:56.58,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Is he ignoring me, knowing I'm here?}Chủ nhân nhận ra nhưng vẫn bơ mình?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:16:00.92,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Or has he lost interest in me?}Hay hết hứng thú với mình rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:04.55,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Lilith...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:06.83,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Um...}Chuyện là...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:09.51,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Here...}Đây...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.54,0:16:12.39,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{A dismissal notice!}Thông báo sa thải?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.27,0:16:14.82,sign_23144_211_Open_House_Day,Text,0,0,0,,{Open House Day}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:18.58,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,Ngày phụ huynh đến trường?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.86,0:16:25.61,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{M-My teacher said that servants \Noften attend it at our school.}G-Giáo viên nói rằng người hầu thường hay tham gia...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:29.79,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{And you're all I have.}Và nhà mình chỉ có mỗi cô...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:34.04,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{But you're suspicious, \Nand you'll attract attention.}Nhưng cô quá đáng ngờ và thu hút chú ý.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:36.71,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I don't want other people to meet you.}Tôi không muốn cô gặp ai hết.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:44.14,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Thế nên tôi lo lắng không biết phải làm sao...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:45.87,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{So...}Vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:49.57,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm not forcing you, but...}Tôi không ép cô đâu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:53.89,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I hope you come.}Hi vọng cô có thể đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:58.37,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Gladly.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:02.25,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'll take care of it.}Tôi rất sẵn lòng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:04.95,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You'll come?!}Cô sẽ đến hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:06.13,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Of course.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:09.14,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'm glad to hear it.}Tôi rất vui khi nghe nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:12.84,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I thought you'd lost interest in me.}Tôi tưởng chủ nhân hết hứng thú với mình rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.14,0:17:14.84,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Of course not!}Dĩ nhiên là không!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:19.46,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I've been thinking this whole time \Nabout how I could get you to come!}Lúc nào tôi cũng nghĩ về cô cả!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:22.82,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're all I ever think about!}Ngay cả lúc này!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:27.33,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{M-Me, too.}T-Tôi cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:28.72,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Did you say something?}Cô nói gì à?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:33.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\pos(195,163)\frz11\bord0\shad0\c&H49B9F3&\b1}{Smile}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:33.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\frz349\bord0\shad0\c&H49B9F3&\b1\pos(497,163)}{Oh, my}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:33.81,sign_24968_234_The_Maid_I_Hired,Text,0,0,0,,{The }{\fs30\c&H953CA0&}{Maid }{\c\fs26}{I Hired Recently\NIs }{\fs30\c&H953CA0&}{Mysterious}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:33.82,Top Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{The Maid I Hired Recently Is Mysterious.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:42.56,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Listen up, Lilith.}Nghe đây Lilith.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:48.45,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Both the teachers and the parents at \Nthe school I go to are very strict.}Cả giáo viên lẫn phụ huynh\N trường tôi học đều rất khó tính.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:50.79,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You know what I'm trying to tell you, right?}Cô hiểu ý tôi chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:55.61,Flashback - Sus Maid,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You want me to be more strict with you.}Ngài muốn tôi phải khó tính phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:56.89,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That's not it at all!}Không phải!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:58.39,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It's your outfit!}Đồng phục của cô!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.10,0:18:01.77,Flashback - Sus Maid,Lilith,0,0,0,,{This is my normal maid outfit.}Đây là đồ hầu gái bình thường mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:04.70,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It's not normal.}Vậy mà bình thường hả...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:05.98,Flashback - Sus Maid,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Understood.}Đã rõ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.34,0:18:09.67,Flashback - Sus Maid,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'll dress up as fancy as I can.}Tôi sẽ ăn mặc thật nổi bật.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:11.16,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That's no better!}Không được!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:13.84,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You'll make not just me, but my \Nwhole class obsessed with you!}Như thế cả lớp nhìn cô mất!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:15.38,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It'll collapse the school!}Trường học sẽ náo loạn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:17.97,Flashback - Sus Maid,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Don't you think that's a \Nbit of an overstatement?}Tôi không nghĩ đến mức đó đâu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:22.61,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{In any case, please come to the \Nopen house in normal clothing.}Tóm lại mặc thật bình thường thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:29.86,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{This one's too dull.}Bộ này có hơi nhàm chán.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:34.40,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{The back is too exposed on this one.}Bộ này thì hở lưng quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:39.17,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{This one might get me \Nscolded by the young master.}Bộ này chủ nhân mắng mình nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:42.81,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{What should I do?}Làm sao giờ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:52.38,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I hope Lilith isn't going to miss it because \Nshe doesn't have any other clothes.}Không biết Lilith có đến không...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:58.99,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I was just glad I was able to tell \Nher there was an open house.}Chỉ cần nói cho cô ấy về buổi hôm nay là đủ rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:07.15,Flashback - Sus Maid,Dad,0,0,0,,{Sorry.}Xin lỗi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:11.24,Flashback - Sus Maid,Dad,0,0,0,,{Mom and I have some very important \Nwork that we have to attend to.}Ba mẹ có công việc quan trọng phải làm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:13.78,Flashback - Sus Maid,Mom,0,0,0,,{Do good, Yuuri.}Cố lên nhé Yuuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:32.52,Main,Kid A,0,0,0,,{It's just my mom coming.}Chỉ có mẹ tớ đến thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:34.40,Main,Kid B,0,0,0,,{Both of my parents are coming.}Ba mẹ tớ đều đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:41.35,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,{Everyone, take your seats, please.}Các em, ngồi vào chỗ nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:42.81,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,{Class is starting.}Lớp học bắt đầu rồi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.17,0:19:45.81,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,{Parents and guardians, please enter.}Xin mời phụ huynh và người giám hộ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:57.17,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{She doesn't have to come.}Không cần phải đến đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:19:59.43,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Mình vẫn ổn thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:01.53,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{She's too suspicious.}Cô ấy quá đáng ngờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:05.88,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{So why was I hoping she'd come?}Nhưng tại sao mình lại mong chờ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:26.16,Flashback - Sus Maid,Lilith,0,0,0,,{My apologies.}Xin thứ lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:29.44,Flashback - Sus Maid,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You were the only one I could ask.}Cô là người duy nhất tôi có thể nhờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:32.53,Flashback - Sus Maid,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Thank you, Fujisaki-san.}Cảm ơn, Fujisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:35.96,Flashback - Sus Maid,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{It's not a big deal at all.}Có gì đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:49.14,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I apologize for arriving late today.}Xin lỗi vì tôi đến trễ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:51.90,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It took longer to prepare than I expected.}Mất thời gian chuẩn bị hơn tôi nghĩ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:53.31,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:56.85,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You were working hard today.}Hôm nay chủ nhân đã rất cố gắng nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:20:58.76,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:03.73,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Why won't you look at me?}Sao ngài không nhìn qua đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:09.40,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master?}Chủ nhân?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:13.45,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Thanks for coming today.}Cảm ơn vì đã đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:14.77,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You made me happy.}Cô làm tôi vui lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.64,0:21:24.42,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Thank you, too.}Tôi cũng vậy, cảm ơn chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.71,0:23:07.22,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{School was more exhausting than usual.}Trường học có vẻ mệt mỏi hơn bình thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.77,0:23:10.79,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Lilith.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.79,0:23:12.91,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{There's something I forgot to tell you.}Tôi quên chưa nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:14.72,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{What is it, young master?}Là gì ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.97,0:23:17.23,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You looked good in that outfit, too.}Bộ đó cũng hợp với cô lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.43,0:23:24.60,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{What am I to do with you, young master?}Đúng là không thể đỡ được cậu chủ mà.
